<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About St. Andrews Heights</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">St. Andrews Heights is a short distance from Kensington Business Revitalization Zone, home to famous restaurants include Broken Plate Greek restaurant, Kensington Pub, and Oolong Tea House. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">North of the community is the Norma Bush and Father David Bauer Arenas.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">St. Andrews Heights is located in Ward 7 of the Calgary City Council. The estimated population is 1,470.</p>
